06:56.003 --> 06:57.286
Hey.

06:57.288 --> 06:59.455
Catherine.

06:59.457 --> 07:02.642
I wasn't expecting you
to be here so early.

07:02.644 --> 07:04.177
I wasn't expecting you

07:04.179 --> 07:05.762
to be here at all.
Look,

07:05.764 --> 07:07.930
I've been meaning
to talk to you.

07:07.932 --> 07:10.984
Actually, I just
figured it out myself.

07:10.986 --> 07:12.068
You brought calla lilies.

07:12.070 --> 07:13.403
The other day, when you

07:13.405 --> 07:15.488
mentioned your
mother's necklace.

07:15.490 --> 07:18.524
My doctor, when I was a kid,

07:18.526 --> 07:19.993
I called her Vanessa.

07:19.995 --> 07:21.477
I never knew
her last name,

07:21.479 --> 07:23.746
but she had the
same necklace.

07:23.748 --> 07:25.698
My mom was your doctor?

07:25.700 --> 07:27.367
I was too stunned
to tell you.

07:27.369 --> 07:29.535
Oh, my God.

07:29.537 --> 07:31.654
Those...

07:31.656 --> 07:35.291
those experiments
that Muirfield did on you

07:35.293 --> 07:37.794
and those...
those other orphaned kids,

07:37.796 --> 07:39.512
did she perform them?
No.

07:39.514 --> 07:42.382
No, you think I'd be here
with flowers if she had?

07:42.384 --> 07:45.101
I'm here with flowers,
and I'm conflicted about her.

07:45.103 --> 07:46.936
Catherine, your mother
wasn't the one

07:46.938 --> 07:48.438
who experimented on us.

07:48.440 --> 07:50.273
She was the doctor who
came in to check on us

07:50.275 --> 07:51.858
and made sure we were okay.

07:51.860 --> 07:54.527
Honestly, she was
the only truly

07:54.529 --> 07:57.397
loving adult we had,
and I adored her.

07:57.399 --> 07:59.115
That's why I came here today.

07:59.117 --> 08:00.683
But I am sorry

08:00.685 --> 08:02.235
if my being here has upset you.

08:02.237 --> 08:03.786
No.

08:03.788 --> 08:05.988
Um...

08:05.990 --> 08:08.207
today is supposed to be

08:08.209 --> 08:11.044
about celebrating her.

08:11.046 --> 08:14.547
Well, there was
lots to celebrate.

08:14.549 --> 08:17.083
You know she used
to bring us art supplies

08:17.085 --> 08:18.084
to keep us busy.

08:18.086 --> 08:20.720
God, I probably

08:20.722 --> 08:23.306
grew up eating
your leftovers,

08:23.308 --> 08:24.757
watching your
old movies.

08:24.759 --> 08:27.009
That's where all my old
VHS tapes probably

08:27.011 --> 08:28.594
disappeared to.
<i>Airplane,</i>

08:28.596 --> 08:30.646
all the Pink Panthers.

08:30.648 --> 08:33.982
"I thought you said
your dog did not bite".

08:33.985 --> 08:35.400
"That is not my dog."

08:36.938 --> 08:39.355
She had a pretty good
sense of humor

08:39.357 --> 08:40.740
for a biochemist.

08:43.659 --> 08:44.994
Um,

08:44.996 --> 08:46.446
my family,

08:46.448 --> 08:47.947
we're, uh, having a thing

08:47.949 --> 08:49.082
for her tonight.

08:49.084 --> 08:51.918
Just-just small,
if you want to come.

08:51.920 --> 08:53.503
I would love to come.

08:53.505 --> 08:56.089
I'll see if I can
find some of those old

08:56.091 --> 08:57.623
VHS tapes.

08:59.209 --> 09:01.210
If it's all right with you, I'd
like to do something for her.

09:01.212 --> 09:03.579
Maybe replace the headstone.

09:03.581 --> 09:05.598
I noticed it was cracked.

09:05.600 --> 09:08.217
Looks like it's been
that way for a while.

09:08.219 --> 09:09.752
The crack's pretty deep.

09:09.754 --> 09:12.638
Did you guys
have her moved?

09:12.640 --> 09:13.890
No.

09:13.892 --> 09:16.058
I mean, at least
I don't think so.

09:16.060 --> 09:17.777
But then again, I am always

09:17.779 --> 09:19.645
the last person
to know these things

09:19.647 --> 09:21.147
when it comes to my mom.

09:21.149 --> 09:22.198
You know what?

09:22.200 --> 09:23.783
It's beautiful as is.

09:23.785 --> 09:25.735
Maybe I'll make a donation
to her favorite charity.

09:25.737 --> 09:27.403
Just come over tonight

09:27.405 --> 09:29.288
and listen to '80s
power ballads.

09:29.290 --> 09:30.823
That is charity enough.

09:30.825 --> 09:32.608
I like '80s power ballads.

09:36.748 --> 09:38.447
I'll give you
some privacy.

09:38.449 --> 09:40.466
I'll see you at the
park dedication?

09:40.468 --> 09:42.301
Yeah.

09:50.594 --> 09:52.562
Vincent?

09:59.820 --> 10:01.904
Vincent?

10:03.740 --> 10:05.775
Vincent?

